HELP		[0 or 1 argument]

Displays help information to explain the system commands.

HELP

	Displays a list of all commands and a brief
	summary of their purpose.

HELP str1

	Displays a detailed explanation of the command designated
	by str1.  str1 must be a valid command.  It may be an
	intrinsic command or an alias, and it may be abbreviated.

